{"tid":620047,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強國怪風】全球最大6噸秦始皇銅像竟吹塌 網民：暗示「帝制」倒台？","createTime":"2018-04-07T08:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T09:02:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"638ac3902ed63196a16b4249d10ea44904425211","tid":620047,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:43:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180407/large/1523065097_7dab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180407%2Flarge%2F1523065097_7dab.jpg&h=2ca487ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 山東省濱州市一座高19米、重6噸，號稱全球最大的秦始皇銅像，昨日在強風下被吹倒，無人受傷。這雖然是一宗普通的事故，但內地網民即時聯想到解除任期限制、形同稱帝的習近平，他們留言暗諷：「專制帝王抵抗不住春風！」「老天爺也看不下去了！」「暗示&hellip;&hellip;倒台！」「凶兆，某人怕不怕？」「獨裁者逆天而立，倒是天意！」<br />\n<br />\n內地媒體報道，濱州昨日狂風大作，當地氣象局發出大風黃色預警，這座於2005年9月建成的秦始皇銅像，「在狂風助力下，騰空而起，飛出數十米，被吹倒在地面目全非，銅製的冕旒也散落了一地」。報道又稱，由於銅像實在太大，「當地工作人員都束手無策」，銅像臉部嚴重破壞，被完全壓扁，最後工作人員用拖車將殘骸拖走。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民把消滅六國、高度集權、焚書坑儒的秦始皇，聯想到剛剛登基的「習帝」，說這銅像被吹倒「好像寓意不太好」，更有網民稱這是「凶兆」，「老天爺也看不下去了」，更多網民稱事件後，「趕緊報告『黃』上」，「省長的位子懸了」。網民的意件實在太過激烈，社交媒體上很多都已經不能再留言評論。<br />\n<br />\n網民意見：<br />\n<br />\n希雅士：暗示集權者會&hellip;&hellip;倒？<br />\n<br />\nsaltwater_river：暗示皇權倒台！<br />\n<br />\nQwerty_122：哈哈，凶兆。某人怕不怕？<br />\n<br />\n凜冬將至醉意漸濃：暗示帝制被吹翻！<br />\n<br />\n初學者的未知數：多行不義必自斃！<br />\n<br />\n一個跳大神兒的：專制帝王抵抗不住春風！<br />\n<br />\nsina的浪：老天爺也看不下去了！<br />\n<br />\n娜金拉措就是sunny：好像寓意不太好&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n桅儂：同治的都倒了，磚制的能不倒嗎？<br />\n<br />\n舞毛苟的靈道：糾結，我該說好還是不好呢？請指示&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\naaappp65：省長的位子懸了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n雲裳花容露華濃：趕緊報告黃上！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180407/58043424\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180407%2F58043424&d=oOx0PQo6li7FOOuXmjG%2ByP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=12f14b17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180407%2F58043424&h=659fafd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180407/58043424</a>"},{"pid":"7b3195b746556a65f624c63cc5f02c9c650df14d","tid":620047,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:46:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b53c439ecd4659b1fa3f76b54a395ce3e12287","tid":620047,"uid":14073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:49:17.000Z","msg":"係咪王莽做嘅？"},{"pid":"b509947a37ef461cfe0f8d16d64177b072f75787","tid":620047,"uid":38671,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:50:21.000Z","msg":"別高興  別以為叫始祖"},{"pid":"cde292116eb29f132d3c2be4129800ba77b54da2","tid":620047,"uid":6869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:53:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a5f2ee112e37e5594921d6ae90c5aaedcdd1dfe","tid":620047,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b509947a37ef461cfe0f8d16d64177b072f75787","tid":620047,"uid":38671,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:50:21.000Z","msg":"別高興  別以為叫始祖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:54:06.000Z","msg":"真係啱晒比維尼聽下"},{"pid":"5510279b30e5b94192f83e5bdc9d013583cc12a5","tid":620047,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:54:17.000Z","msg":"假大空<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23b9ce3a5dcde4cfa08955bb7dfd0215185d13c","tid":620047,"uid":35014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:56:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ba5e66b51a307ed4a0dc1a96e9e670abba8bd93","tid":620047,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T09:00:53.000Z","msg":"同治的，磚製的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0bf9c56d1a2cab874b9814895fe984ba346d45",